org.osmdroid.views.overlay

Class OverlayItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osmdroid.views.overlay.OverlayItem

  • public class OverlayItem
extends Object
    An Item that can be displayed in a ItemizedOverlay or ItemizedIconOverlay. Immutable class describing a GeoPoint with a Title and a Description.
